 written in the Torah: As you judge others, so are you judged. As you reap, so shall you sow.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li-Abi H\u0323a\u0304tim 78 \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u062d\u0627\u062a\u0645 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062f\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064d \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u00a0\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0643\u0652\u062a\u064f\u0648\u0628\u064c \u0641\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29235,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/12\/rifq-dunya-benefit-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":25060,"position":1},"title":"Qays on Rifq: Whoever is gentle in the world benefits in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Waki\u2019 reported: Qays, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIt is said that whoever has the quality of gentleness, it will benefit him in the Hereafter.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 25309 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0643\u0650\u064a\u0639\u064c \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0633\u064d \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u064a\u064f\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064f\u0624\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u0650\u0641\u0652\u0642\u064e \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u064f\u0646\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0622\u062e\u0650\u0631\u064e\u0629\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/09\/11\/rahmah-compassion-for-children\/","url_meta":{"origin":25060,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: The Prophet is merciful to his children","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 11, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: Al-Aqra' ibn Habis saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, kissing his grandson Al-Hasan. He said, \u201cI have ten children and I do not kiss any of them.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, whoever does not show mercy will not receive mercy.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5997,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8217,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/prophet-described-tawrat-torah\/","url_meta":{"origin":25060,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tawrat: The Prophet&#8217;s description in the Torah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ata' ibn Yasar reported: I met Abdullah ibn Amr, may Allah be pleased with him, and I said, \u201cTell me about the description of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, in the Torah.\u201d Abdullah said, \u201cBy Allah, he is described in the Torah with some of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25107,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/07\/24\/urwah-no-iman-cannot-trust\/","url_meta":{"origin":25060,"position":4},"title":"Urwah on Trust: No faith for one who cannot be trusted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham ibn 'Urwah reported: 'Urwah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cBe not deceived by the prayer of a man, nor by his fasting. Whoever wills can fast and whoever wills can pray, yet there is no religion for one who cannot be trusted.\u201d Source: al-\u012ama\u0304n li Ibn Abi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38423,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/11\/01\/rahmah-khatam-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":25060,"position":5},"title":"Mujahid on Quran: Mercy descends upon finishing the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 1, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Hakam reported: Mujahid, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cMercy descends at the time of completing the entire Quran.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 30042 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0645\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u062c\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064f \u062a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0632\